page.title: 14Brownies & Leisure. Woking.
page.content: Georgina lives in Faris Lane. I go to Brownies on Wednesdays. We meet in the Church Hall at West Byfleet and have: inspection, fun in the Park, games, songs, book work, badge work, visits, coffee mornings and enrolment. At the moment I am doing my Friendship badge and my Pet Lovers badge. For this badge I have to look after my pet goldfish for three months. I am also doing a 75 year booklet and filling in miles. On Sundays we go for walks at Pyrford Woods, on the Golf Course or by the Canal. Also we go to Church at Pyrford and my brother Andrew and I go to Sunday School. In September we will go into the Explorers which is a higher class. Sometimes we play tennis at Halstead at weekends. Occasionally Daddy takes our garden waste to the rubbish tip in Martyr's Lane.
